headline: Homes.com Report: U.S. Home Price Growth Remained Muted at 2.4% in August as the Market Shifts Toward Buyers
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., September 09, 2025--Homes.com, a CoStar Group leading online residential marketplace, released a new report today analyzing home price trends in August (based on the data collected to date), including price trends across major metros and house types.
